2: convert into Base64 encoded SVG :   https://www.utilities-online.info/base64?utm_source=buildspace.so&utm_medium=buildspace_project

3: image:   data:image/svg+xml;base64,INSERT_YOUR_BASE64_ENCODED_SVG_HERE

4: creat Json with base64 using point 2 

5: json:  data:application/json;base64,INSERT_YOUR_BASE64_ENCODED_JSON_HERE



