#Web3Modal
1: npm install --save web3modal
2: for WalletConnect        => npm install --save @walletconnect/web3-provider
3: for BinanceChain wallet  => no need to install anything
4: for coinbase(WalletLink) => npm install --save @coinbase/wallet-sdk
import everything in App.js => const providerOptions => 